# Pulse — Social Mock Trading App

**Root:** `simvest/` · **Package:** `pulse` v1.0.3 · **Bundle:** `com.pulse.app` · **Firebase:** `pulse-app-real`

Mobile-first social paper-trading for Gen Z. Users get **$10,000 virtual cash**, trade at real market prices, compete on a leaderboard, and share ideas in a feed. No real money.

## Stack

- **Frontend:** React Native 0.81 + Expo 54, React 19, TypeScript
- **Backend:** Firebase Auth (email/password) + Firestore
- **Quotes/charts:** Yahoo Finance chart API (primary, 60s cache)
- **Search/news:** Finnhub (client rate limiting in `finnhubRateLimit.ts`)
- **AI:** Groq `llama-3.1-8b-instant` via `aiExplainService.ts` (keys in `src/config/apiKeys.ts`)
- **Functions:** Firebase Cloud Functions v2 — `onReferralClaimCreated` pays referrers

## Navigation (custom tabs, no React Navigation)

`App.tsx` owns state. Tabs via `BottomNavbar`: **home**, **search**, **leaderboard**, **portfolio**, **profile**. Overlays: post detail, user profile, settings, notifications (price alerts), post-signup onboarding.

Auth: `LoginScreen` → optional `PostSignupOnboardingScreen` (`onboardingCompleted === false`) → main app. Login accepts email or username (`loginUsernames` collection). Wrapped in `AuthProvider` + `VersionGate` (Firestore `appConfig` min version).

## Firestore model

```
users/{uid}                    — profile, cash, XP, level, achievements, tags
  portfolio/{symbol}           — positions
  tradingHistory/{id}          — buy/sell records
  priceAlerts/{id}             — above/below alerts
  portfolioSnapshots/{id}      — performance chart history
  blockedUsers/{blockedId}
posts/{postId}                 — feed (likes, saves, reposts, $TICKER tags)
  comments/{commentId}
loginUsernames/{usernameKey}   — username → email (pre-auth lookup)
referralCodes/{code}           — code → referrer UID
referrals/{uid}                — referrer stats
referralClaims/{claimId}       — pending payouts (Cloud Function processes)
appConfig/{docId}              — min version, store URLs (read-only)
```

**Portfolio math:** `totalPortfolioValue = cash + sum(positions.totalValue)`. Starting cash: **$10,000** (`STARTING_CASH` in `src/constants/theme.ts`).

## Key features (implemented)

- **Trading:** buy/sell via `tradingService.ts`, no fees, weighted avg cost
- **Feed:** posts with ticker auto-detect, like/save/repost/comment, block/report
- **Gamification:** XP (+10/trade, +25/winning sell), 15 levels, achievements (`gamificationService.ts`)
- **Leaderboard:** top 100 by `totalReturn` (`userService.getLeaderboard`)
- **Referrals:** +$200 new user & referrer; claims → Cloud Function payout
- **Price alerts:** polled every 50s in `App.tsx`; bell badge for unacknowledged hits
- **AI explain:** stock (Search) + portfolio (12/day limit)
- **Settings:** portfolio reset to $10k, privacy toggle, account deletion

## Services (`src/services/`)

`userService`, `tradingService`, `stockPriceService`, `chartDataService`, `stockSearchService`, `marketDataService`, `postsService`, `gamificationService`, `referralService`, `priceAlertsService`, `aiExplainService`, `blockService`, `notificationService`, `appVersionService`, `accountDeletionService`

## UI theme

Dark-first: bg `#0F1419`, primary `#8B5CF6`, success `#10B981`, error `#EF4444`. Tokens in `src/constants/theme.ts`.

