## Conventions

- Match existing service/class patterns; minimal diffs
- Username login via `loginUsernames`; referral bonus constants must stay in sync with `functions/index.js`
- Stock prices: prefer `stockPriceService` (Yahoo); don't add unnecessary API layers
- Firestore rules changes: deploy via `npm run deploy:firestore-rules`
